descriptionNullable:
Dataset for the classification of waste in the body of the vehicle.
For your convenience, this task can be solved using 2 methods: classification (folder "cargo_classification") and detection (folder "cargo_detection").

There are 2179 images in total in the dataset. You should divide it into a training and validation sample in any way that is convenient for you.
